Although,
 Lambda fields are not widely used in risk aware path planning due to the complexity of constant integrals.
 The utilisation of the framework in multi-robot decision making,
 allows robotic agents to compare physical risks between heterogeneous locomotion types that are affected differently depending on the environmental setup;
 providing accurate real world assessments for robot fleet coordination and task management.
